  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective study of patients with stroke with accompanying motor and visual
      deficits. There will be patients' evaluations at 2 time points at the acute and subacute
      period after the stroke. Statistical correlation of the improvement of their deficits will
      be conducted
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
